Jumping Jokers

If you're a fan of the classic Novomatic universe, you'll love the simplicity of the Jumping Joker fruit slot. This colorful game is perfect for players who don't need bonus features, as the dynamic expanding wild symbols offer plenty of excitement. The goal is to land the jumping joker on as many reels as possible in a single spin for big results. Read on for more details!

Setup and Symbols

This Novomatic slot is fairly simple, with a collection of fruit symbols spinning around simple purple reels. The gameplay consists of 5 reels and 5 fixed paylines, and can be played for 40 cents to 100 euros per spin on desktop, mobile, and tablet devices. Visually, Jumping Jokers is set against a purple background with navy blue reels. At the bottom of the paytable are the following icons:

-Grape, lemon, and orange icons - Get 3, 4, or 5 of these and win a prize of 0.5, 1, or 5 times your bet;
-Plum and grape icons - These offer payouts of 1, 2, or 10 times your bet;
-Bell icon - Offers payouts of 2, 5, or 20 times your bet;
-Melon icon - Offers payouts of 3, 8, or 30 times your bet;
-The best of the standard symbols is the Gold Star, which pays out 10, 50, or 100 times your bet if you get 3, 4, or 5 in a combination.

Special Symbols

The Jumping Joker is the wild symbol and can land on all 5 reels. When it does, it expands to fill the entire wild reel. Even better, if the Joker lands on multiple reels, they will all become wild!

The Golden Crown is the Mystery Scatter - land 3 or more crowns and you'll win a special prize from the following ranges:

-3 scatters pay between 2 and 100 times your bet;
-4 scatters pay between 10 and 500 times your bet;
-5 scatters pay between 100 and 1,000 times your total bet.

Conclusion

The most exciting part of this free slot in our ADM casino library is undoubtedly the Mystery Scatters. I had my biggest wins from expanding wilds when I got 4 reels completely wild, which brought me a win of about 400 times my bet. Another positive aspect of this game is its medium-high variance, ideal for a smooth and uncomplicated game. If you're looking for fruit slots with more free spins and better graphics, Novomatic has many options, but get started with these favorites:

-Supra Hot
-Sizzling 6
-Mega Joker

